PN,36101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,FThe UK's biggest defence company has
OL,7,Frevealed the first uncrewed fighter
OL,8,Fjet built for the country.
OL,10,FThe prototype aircraft has been
OL,11,Fdesigned and built by engineers at BAE
OL,12,FSystems in Warton, Lancashire, home of
OL,13,Fthe UK's sovereign combat air
OL,14,Findustrial capability.
OL,16,FThe company has revealed a model of
OL,17,Fits new self flying jet, the
OL,18,FCollaborative Combat Aircraft (CCA),
OL,19,Fwhich is designed to compliment
OL,20,Fexisting crewed aircraft.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
