FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,FThe first CCA named Brontanax, derived
OL,7,Ffrom the ancient Greek words for
OL,8,Fthunder and king, is to provide
OL,9,Felectronic warfare and precision
OL,10,Fstrike capabilities against airborne
OL,11,Fand ground targets .
OL,13,FMore than 500 employees have been
OL,14,Finvolved in the aircraft's development
OL,15,Fto date, working with over 75 large
OL,16,Fcompanies.
OL,18,FIt is designed to extend combat mass
OL,19,Ffor armed forces and is planned to
OL,20,Fenter service before the end of the
OL,21,Fdecade.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,FDefence Secretary Wes Streeting MP
OL,7,Fsaid: "The unveiling of Brontanax, the
OL,8,FUK's first uncrewed autonomous
OL,9,FCollaborative Combat Aircraft, is a
OL,10,Ftestament to the extraordinary talent
OL,11,Fand innovation across our sovereign
OL,12,Fdefence industry.
OL,14,F"Built at BAE Systems in Warton by
OL,15,FBritish engineers, backed by British
OL,16,Fbusinesses large and small, this
OL,17,Faircraft demonstrates that the UK has
OL,18,Fthe skills, the technology and the
OL,19,Fdetermination to lead the world in
OL,20,Fcombat air power.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,F"We're investing #300 million in our
OL,7,FStormFighter programme to develop an
OL,8,Fautonomous combat aircraft here in the
OL,9,FUK. This launch shows the depth of
OL,10,Findustrial capability we have here in
OL,11,FBritain to help deliver our ambition
OL,12,Fto become Europe's first sixth
OL,13,Fgeneration air force."
OL,15,FSimon Barnes, Group Managing Director
OL,16,Fof BAE Systems' Air sector said the
OL,17,Fadvancement "builds on our long-
OL,18,Fstanding commitment to innovation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
