OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,FHe said: "We recognise armed forces
OL,7,Fare being challenged to meet the
OL,8,Fdemands of speed, adaptability and
OL,9,Fscale. Our Collaborative Combat
OL,10,FAircraft will provide the ability to
OL,11,Fextend the reach of crewed aircraft,
OL,12,Fgenerating greater combat mass at
OL,13,Flower cost, while keeping pilots out
OL,14,Fof harm's way.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
