PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784722709
OL,3,CFirst uncrewed fighter jet built by
OL,4,Cengineers revealed
OL,6,F"This capability represents a
OL,7,Fsignificant company investment in the
OL,8,FUK's future of air power and builds on
OL,9,Four long-standing commitment to
OL,10,Finnovation. Alongside supporting
OL,11,Fdefence priorities, it will strengthen
OL,12,Fthe UK's sovereign defence ecosystem
OL,13,Fby creating opportunities for SMEs,
OL,14,Fsuppliers and partners across the
OL,15,Fcountry."
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
